Dialogue: 2,0:00:00.00,0:00:02.52,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}第三话
Dialogue: 2,0:00:02.52,0:00:05.12,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}小小的牺牲
Dialogue: 2,0:00:06.50,0:00:13.57,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}好像又有人被从城市流放了
Dialogue: 2,0:00:13.57,0:00:21.97,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}虽然矿山有几处是不准进入的
Dialogue: 2,0:00:21.97,0:00:29.37,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}但听说那人无视进去后引起了塌方事故
Dialogue: 2,0:00:30.72,0:00:32.70,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}还有
Dialogue: 2,0:00:32.70,0:00:34.90,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}对了
Dialogue: 2,0:00:34.90,0:00:39.97,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}以前有人曾去调查过那花
Dialogue: 2,0:00:39.97,0:00:46.55,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}听说有一部分魔物很讨厌那花
Dialogue: 2,0:00:46.55,0:00:55.02,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}也就是说那花有驱逐魔物的效果
Dialogue: 2,0:00:56.17,0:01:04.90,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}以前有人曾去调查过那花
Dialogue: 2,0:01:04.90,0:01:13.07,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不过不知道为什么被城市永久的流放了……
Dialogue: 2,0:01:14.97,0:01:22.37,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}哦，有驱逐魔物的效果？

Dialogue: 2,0:01:23.07,0:01:29.77,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}哎，涅尔弗雷纳先生订购了啊
Dialogue: 2,0:01:29.77,0:01:37.65,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}明明很贵，但却订了很多
Dialogue: 2,0:01:37.97,0:01:43.60,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}也不觉得可惜
Dialogue: 2,0:01:43.60,0:01:49.35,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}在游行时都发给大家了。
Dialogue: 2,0:01:49.67,0:01:56.62,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}那时候只有我没领到
Dialogue: 2,0:01:57.12,0:01:59.12,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}但是
Dialogue: 2,0:01:59.12,0:02:03.37,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}桑克瑞德先生
Dialogue: 2,0:02:03.37,0:02:09.27,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我是不能接受这样的礼物的
Dialogue: 2,0:02:09.27,0:02:15.50,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}仅仅是你的歌声就填满了我的胸口
Dialogue: 2,0:02:15.82,0:02:17.82,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不不
Dialogue: 2,0:02:17.82,0:02:24.97,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}如你一般的柔弱女子
Dialogue: 2,0:02:24.97,0:02:32.50,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不用这花儿保护怎么行
Dialogue: 2,0:02:32.87,0:02:37.65,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}与帝国的战争即将临近……
Dialogue: 2,0:02:37.65,0:02:43.20,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}这传闻如果是真的
Dialogue: 2,0:02:43.20,0:02:49.30,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}这里说不定就会变成战场
Dialogue: 2,0:02:49.52,0:02:51.52,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}啊
Dialogue: 2,0:02:51.52,0:02:55.95,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}说起来那件事的话
Dialogue: 2,0:02:55.95,0:03:05.47,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}似乎现在正在呼吁着乌尔达哈的权势的继承者们啊
Dialogue: 2,0:03:05.80,0:03:17.87,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}听说还得到信息说乌尔达哈中潜进了帝国的密探
Dialogue: 2,0:03:18.15,0:03:21.72,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}继承者们……
Dialogue: 2,0:03:21.72,0:03:25.42,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}比如说？
Dialogue: 2,0:03:26.00,0:03:32.40,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}涅尔弗雷纳先生也是其中一人吧
Dialogue: 2,0:03:32.40,0:03:40.00,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}他是艾斯泰姆珠宝店的社长家的儿子
Dialogue: 2,0:03:40.00,0:03:50.22,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}就连店的主人罗罗力特议员大人也非常看好他
Dialogue: 2,0:03:50.55,0:03:54.27,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}原来如此
Dialogue: 2,0:03:54.27,0:04:06.30,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}涅尔弗雷纳先生经常出去聚会吧
Dialogue: 2,0:04:06.70,0:04:19.67,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}那是乌尔达哈权势的继承者们讨论“如何与帝国战斗”的聚会
Dialogue: 2,0:04:24.02,0:04:32.82,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}从这里往西有个很大的游乐场对吧？
Dialogue: 2,0:04:32.82,0:04:42.57,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}游乐场“白金幻象”就是他们的聚集场所吧？

Dialogue: 2,0:04:42.85,0:04:46.95,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}“白金幻象”！
Dialogue: 2,0:04:46.95,0:04:58.17,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}只有乌尔达哈才有的华丽与豪奢之声！

Dialogue: 2,0:05:02.35,0:05:04.35,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}啊啊
Dialogue: 2,0:05:04.35,0:05:09.22,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}突然想出一首歌
Dialogue: 2,0:05:09.22,0:05:14.95,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}抱歉先走一步！
Dialogue: 2,0:05:30.55,0:05:35.85,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}……你等一下
Dialogue: 2,0:05:35.85,0:05:37.85,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}对了
Dialogue: 2,0:05:37.85,0:05:45.40,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我忘记给你劝告了。
Dialogue: 2,0:05:46.02,0:05:56.82,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}: 在娱乐殿堂“白金幻象”现在正在雇佣保镖
Dialogue: 2,0:05:56.82,0:06:02.87,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}因为也收冒险者，
Dialogue: 2,0:06:02.87,0:06:14.22,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你到附近的事务所接待处去看看怎么样？

Dialogue: 2,0:06:14.65,0:06:22.35,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}因为是解决金钱纠纷的工作
Dialogue: 2,0:06:22.35,0:06:32.17,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}能认识从有钱人到穷人等各式各样的人哦
Dialogue: 2,0:06:32.55,0:06:40.80,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}与人的相遇能生出赚钱的机会
Dialogue: 2,0:06:40.80,0:06:51.00,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}哎哟
Dialogue: 2,0:07:02.77,0:07:04.77,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}哎哟
Dialogue: 2,0:07:04.77,0:07:06.77,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}客人
Dialogue: 2,0:07:06.77,0:07:13.00,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}您是第一次来吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:07:13.45,0:07:23.62,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我为能记住所有来过游乐场的客人的脸而自豪
Dialogue: 2,0:07:23.92,0:07:25.92,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}顺便
Dialogue: 2,0:07:25.92,0:07:29.05,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}那边的屋子
Dialogue: 2,0:07:29.05,0:07:33.95,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}各种费用非常高，
Dialogue: 2,0:07:33.95,0:07:39.70,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}而且是会员制的
Dialogue: 2,0:07:40.00,0:07:48.35,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不过如果客人您想参加的话
Dialogue: 2,0:07:48.35,0:07:59.25,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}因为有乌尔达哈的权贵们在这里出入
Dialogue: 2,0:07:59.25,0:08:04.72,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我可以为你介绍哟？
Dialogue: 2,0:08:05.45,0:08:06.97,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}作弊！

Dialogue: 2,0:08:06.97,0:08:08.77,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}是你作弊了吧？！

Dialogue: 2,0:08:08.92,0:08:10.92,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}哎？！
Dialogue: 2,0:08:10.92,0:08:15.10,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}怎、怎么会？！

Dialogue: 2,0:08:22.27,0:08:34.62,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}没可能5回连着拿到这张牌！

Dialogue: 2,0:08:34.62,0:08:40.90,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你做了什么？！

Dialogue: 2,0:08:41.30,0:08:43.30,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}哎呀呀。

Dialogue: 2,0:08:43.30,0:08:58.37,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}刚开始我就拒绝你说我是在幸运星下出生的吧？

Dialogue: 2,0:08:58.87,0:09:07.47,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}库库芭，是你动了手脚吧？！
Dialogue: 2,0:09:07.97,0:09:14.42,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我才不会那么做的吧？

Dialogue: 2,0:09:14.42,0:09:21.22,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我也摸不清头脑
Dialogue: 2,0:09:21.22,0:09:33.55,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}而且这里是无法使用任何魔法的地方
Dialogue: 2,0:09:43.15,0:09:46.87,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}输了就是输了。
Dialogue: 2,0:09:46.87,0:09:50.17,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}涅尔弗雷纳
Dialogue: 2,0:09:50.17,0:09:57.32,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}遵守约定吧。
Dialogue: 2,0:09:59.35,0:10:07.60,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}那，快给我讲讲吧
Dialogue: 2,0:10:07.95,0:10:15.75,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你反对与帝国交战
Dialogue: 2,0:10:15.75,0:10:32.50,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}并视察过被帝国占领的东北方的军事都市阿拉米格
Dialogue: 2,0:10:32.85,0:10:41.37,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}听了从阿拉米格来逃难的难民的话
Dialogue: 2,0:10:41.37,0:10:48.62,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}明白了帝国有多么强大
Dialogue: 2,0:10:49.22,0:10:58.47,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}商人们看到了将会到来的商机利益而想引起战争
Dialogue: 2,0:10:58.47,0:11:08.55,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}而战士们不考虑敌人的规模仅为了名誉也想引起战争
Dialogue: 2,0:11:08.87,0:11:15.20,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你想警告那些人们
Dialogue: 2,0:11:15.20,0:11:23.37,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}……这想法我是赞成的
Dialogue: 2,0:11:23.67,0:11:31.55,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}但是做法却太糟糕了。
Dialogue: 2,0:11:31.85,0:11:38.52,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}想引起战争的权势者……

Dialogue: 2,0:11:38.52,0:11:45.45,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}也就是说你们的父亲
Dialogue: 2,0:11:45.45,0:11:48.60,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}母亲们
Dialogue: 2,0:11:48.60,0:12:00.20,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你只是想让他们愁于眼前的事而已
Dialogue: 2,0:12:00.65,0:12:03.70,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}与此同时
Dialogue: 2,0:12:03.70,0:12:09.30,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}使自己的声望提高
Dialogue: 2,0:12:09.30,0:12:19.10,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}作为人民的英雄去得到更强的话语权
Dialogue: 2,0:12:19.50,0:12:22.67,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}是这样吧
Dialogue: 2,0:12:22.67,0:12:27.47,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}游行那事故
Dialogue: 2,0:12:27.47,0:12:37.90,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}是你们造成并且自己收拾的摊子
Dialogue: 2,0:12:38.57,0:12:43.35,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你说什么？！
Dialogue: 2,0:12:43.35,0:12:52.87,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}是这样吗？！

Dialogue: 2,0:12:57.30,0:13:03.65,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你们太小看事故了。
Dialogue: 2,0:13:03.65,0:13:10.32,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}就因为你们这种轻视
Dialogue: 2,0:13:10.32,0:13:19.17,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}使一个人丧了命
Dialogue: 2,0:13:21.40,0:13:28.20,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}死、了？

Dialogue: 2,0:13:28.62,0:13:31.50,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}是啊
Dialogue: 2,0:13:31.50,0:13:36.15,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}留下一个女儿
Dialogue: 2,0:13:36.15,0:13:41.27,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}她没任何亲人
Dialogue: 2,0:13:41.27,0:13:48.04,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}连葬礼都办不起啊
Dialogue: 2,0:13:48.37,0:13:51.46,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}回去了
Dialogue: 2,0:13:51.46,0:14:03.42,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}关于游行的事故没理由受人责备
Dialogue: 2,0:14:08.99,0:14:16.05,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你想把钱扔下就走人吗？

Dialogue: 2,0:14:16.05,0:14:26.28,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}这可没包含在与我的比赛条件里啊？

Dialogue: 2,0:14:26.77,0:14:30.09,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}随你便
Dialogue: 2,0:14:30.09,0:14:38.79,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}给那可怜孩子不也行吗。

Dialogue: 2,0:14:43.68,0:14:46.90,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}那，谢谢了
Dialogue: 2,0:14:46.90,0:14:50.94,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}就这么着吧
Dialogue: 2,0:14:50.94,0:14:55.30,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}科尔吉韦先生
Dialogue: 2,0:14:55.30,0:15:01.17,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}请把这些钱交给那孩子
Dialogue: 2,0:15:01.69,0:15:08.86,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}这、这样好吗？

Dialogue: 2,0:15:09.18,0:15:17.52,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我想要的不是钱而是情报
Dialogue: 2,0:15:17.52,0:15:28.63,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}议会渴望着战争而蠢蠢欲动的、情报
Dialogue: 2,0:15:35.50,0:15:43.68,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}那个，客人啊
Dialogue: 2,0:15:44.10,0:15:51.46,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}您是在那房间里偷听是吗？

Dialogue: 2,0:15:51.46,0:15:56.97,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}因为需要调查
Dialogue: 2,0:15:56.97,0:16:03.68,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}请跟我到接待处来一趟
Dialogue: 2,0:16:33.32,0:16:35.53,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}所以
Dialogue: 2,0:16:35.53,0:16:43.35,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我不打算和任何一方结婚
Dialogue: 2,0:16:43.74,0:16:54.78,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不过一直就这么孤单一人也不行吧？
Dialogue: 2,0:17:02.73,0:17:10.48,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}哥哥……

Dialogue: 2,0:17:13.81,0:17:17.45,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}总、总之
Dialogue: 2,0:17:17.49,0:17:24.39,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}再考虑考虑吧
Dialogue: 2,0:17:24.39,0:17:27.45,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}拉敏
Dialogue: 2,0:17:33.84,0:17:39.15,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我的歌中的“你”
Dialogue: 2,0:17:39.15,0:17:45.01,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}只有一个人哦
Dialogue: 2,0:17:45.96,0:17:51.85,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}……冒险者吗？

Dialogue: 2,0:17:51.85,0:17:56.35,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我听莫莫蒂说了
Dialogue: 2,0:17:56.35,0:18:09.60,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你不是拿着威罗迪纳波斯菊的吗？

Dialogue: 2,0:18:10.09,0:18:19.86,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}那花是只有在边境才能采到的贵重的花
Dialogue: 2,0:18:19.86,0:18:27.58,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}在游行中分发过
Dialogue: 2,0:18:27.94,0:18:29.94,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}但是
Dialogue: 2,0:18:29.94,0:18:40.84,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}一想到那时在游行上发生的事故……

Dialogue: 2,0:18:43.68,0:18:49.21,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}拉敏小姐！

Dialogue: 2,0:18:49.21,0:18:54.82,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}找到了啊！
Dialogue: 2,0:18:54.82,0:18:58.01,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}石头！

Dialogue: 2,0:18:59.25,0:19:03.61,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}啊，是吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:19:03.61,0:19:07.13,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}有才哦
Dialogue: 2,0:19:07.13,0:19:11.66,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}是哪个？

Dialogue: 2,0:19:20.94,0:19:23.35,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你是？

Dialogue: 2,0:19:23.35,0:19:29.08,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我是采矿工阿希莉亚
Dialogue: 2,0:19:29.08,0:19:35.60,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}以后要是想要石头的话
Dialogue: 2,0:19:35.60,0:19:39.34,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}就来找我哦
Dialogue: 2,0:19:40.19,0:19:44.03,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}好厉害呀！
Dialogue: 2,0:19:44.03,0:19:49.69,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}这是猫眼石哦
Dialogue: 2,0:19:49.69,0:19:56.22,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}品质相当不错的石头呢
Dialogue: 2,0:19:56.77,0:20:01.95,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}太好啦！
Dialogue: 2,0:20:17.85,0:20:27.94,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}冒险者你是到处旅行的人是吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:20:28.50,0:20:34.46,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}去过阿拉米格吗？

Dialogue: 2,0:20:34.46,0:20:41.27,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}那是我出生的地方哟！

Dialogue: 2,0:20:41.79,0:20:45.53,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}……啊！

Dialogue: 2,0:20:46.02,0:20:49.05,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不要跑
Dialogue: 2,0:20:49.05,0:20:57.75,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我有话要对你说！

Dialogue: 2,0:20:58.20,0:21:10.45,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我和你父亲都是携带同样使命的人
Dialogue: 2,0:21:10.84,0:21:15.53,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}什么也不要说
Dialogue: 2,0:21:15.53,0:21:18.82,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}拿上这个
Dialogue: 2,0:21:19.57,0:21:22.94,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}讨厌！
Dialogue: 2,0:21:22.94,0:21:27.29,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}杀人犯！
Dialogue: 2,0:21:27.29,0:21:32.57,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}走开！ 
Dialogue: 2,0:21:33.77,0:21:35.24,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不，我只是……

Dialogue: 2,0:21:35.24,0:21:37.13,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}科尔吉韦先生？！
Dialogue: 2,0:21:37.52,0:21:50.81,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不、我只是、那个
Dialogue: 2,0:21:50.81,0:22:05.37,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}……把丧葬费给你……

Dialogue: 2,0:22:05.83,0:22:12.28,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}是这样吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:22:12.28,0:22:17.23,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}但是……

Dialogue: 2,0:22:17.98,0:22:21.75,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}父亲他
Dialogue: 2,0:22:21.82,0:22:31.14,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}还不是被你送进坟墓了嘛！
Dialogue: 2,0:22:31.14,0:22:36.22,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}走开！

Dialogue: 2,0:22:48.76,0:22:51.88,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}对不起
Dialogue: 2,0:22:51.88,0:22:56.54,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}科尔吉韦先生
Dialogue: 2,0:22:56.54,0:23:02.67,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我会好好告诉那孩子的
Dialogue: 2,0:23:02.67,0:23:08.53,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不是科尔吉韦先生的错
Dialogue: 2,0:23:08.89,0:23:10.89,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}唉
Dialogue: 2,0:23:10.89,0:23:16.93,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}那就拜托您了
Dialogue: 2,0:23:16.93,0:23:26.57,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}还有……她现在？

Dialogue: 2,0:23:27.98,0:23:30.29,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}是的
Dialogue: 2,0:23:30.29,0:23:36.38,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我在照顾着那孩子
Dialogue: 2,0:23:36.38,0:23:45.57,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我打算以后也一直跟那个孩子一起生活
Dialogue: 2,0:23:45.89,0:23:49.83,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}那样的话
Dialogue: 2,0:23:49.83,0:23:55.01,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我就放心了
Dialogue: 2,0:24:04.39,0:24:06.39,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}啊
Dialogue: 2,0:24:04.39,0:24:08.37,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}发生了不少事
Dialogue: 2,0:24:08.37,0:24:10.78,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}但是
Dialogue: 2,0:24:10.78,0:24:15.40,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}变成如今这样
Dialogue: 2,0:24:15.08,0:24:19.64,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我也有很大的责任
Dialogue: 2,0:24:20.00,0:24:30.29,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}那孩子的心一定会随着时间而痊愈的吧
Dialogue: 2,0:24:30.29,0:24:33.02,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不过
Dialogue: 2,0:24:33.02,0:24:40.68,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我们还有和平的时间吗…… 
Dialogue: 2,0:24:47.58,0:24:50.52,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}冒险者
Dialogue: 2,0:24:50.52,0:24:56.93,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你听过传闻没有？

Dialogue: 2,0:24:56.93,0:25:06.80,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}即将有危险来到乌尔达哈的传闻
Dialogue: 2,0:25:07.19,0:25:18.11,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}虽然阿希莉亚的父亲从阿拉米格带来了通知
Dialogue: 2,0:25:18.11,0:25:24.52,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}但他已经在事故中过世
Dialogue: 2,0:25:24.52,0:25:31.53,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}详细的情况已经完全不明了
Dialogue: 2,0:25:35.60,0:25:38.46,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}然后……
Dialogue: 2,0:25:38.46,0:25:50.81,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}找你是因为有事求于你。

Dialogue: 2,0:25:51.27,0:26:03.22,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}能帮我调查一下乌尔达哈的纳尔札尔教团自古相传的名叫“咒术”的魔法吗？

Dialogue: 2,0:26:03.22,0:26:14.52,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}听说咒术中有能与死者相会的方法
Dialogue: 2,0:26:14.91,0:26:26.84,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}阿达内斯圣柜堂是接受冒险者们的
Dialogue: 2,0:26:26.84,0:26:41.82,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你的话说不定调查时不会被怀疑
Dialogue: 2,0:26:42.47,0:26:47.75,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}如果困难的话
Dialogue: 2,0:26:47.75,0:26:52.34,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}放弃也没关系
Dialogue: 2,0:26:52.34,0:27:00.16,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我也奇怪那咒术到底存不存在
Dialogue: 2,0:27:00.48,0:27:02.99,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不过
Dialogue: 2,0:27:02.99,0:27:08.46,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}若是得到了什么情报
Dialogue: 2,0:27:08.46,0:27:13.06,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}希望你能告诉我
Dialogue: 2,0:27:13.06,0:27:19.60,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}对于报酬是不吝惜的
Dialogue: 2,0:27:32.21,0:27:38.61,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}万物都有两面性
Dialogue: 2,0:27:38.61,0:27:44.13,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}太阳东升西落
Dialogue: 2,0:27:44.13,0:27:50.00,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}生物终有一死
Dialogue: 2,0:27:51.59,0:27:54.16,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}但是
Dialogue: 2,0:27:54.16,0:28:03.58,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}能否迎来富饶之死则取决于你的心
Dialogue: 2,0:28:03.58,0:28:11.04,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我们愿意为您面临的死亡提供帮助
Dialogue: 2,0:28:11.43,0:28:16.77,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你是冒险者吧
Dialogue: 2,0:28:16.77,0:28:25.99,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我从莫莫蒂大人那里听了介绍
Dialogue: 2,0:28:26.22,0:28:36.25,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}您是想学习乌尔达哈自古相传的神秘之术“咒术”吗
Dialogue: 2,0:28:36.67,0:28:42.08,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}……你说什么？

Dialogue: 2,0:28:42.08,0:28:47.72,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}死者回生之术？
Dialogue: 2,0:28:48.20,0:28:58.27,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你到底被谁灌输了这种东西？！

Dialogue: 2,0:28:58.66,0:29:00.09,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}行了行了~

Dialogue: 2,0:29:00.09,0:29:01.66,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}对咒术产生兴趣~
Dialogue: 2,0:29:01.66,0:29:07.10,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不也是非常值得感~谢的事吗~
Dialogue: 2,0:29:07.10,0:29:15.96,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}穆穆埃珀大导师
Dialogue: 2,0:29:16.05,0:29:22.93,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}死者回生之~术
Dialogue: 2,0:29:22.93,0:29:30.13,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}愿闻其~详
Dialogue: 2,0:29:30.13,0:29:38.46,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}来~到这边来~
Dialogue: 2,0:29:57.32,0:30:00.26,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}好~了
Dialogue: 2,0:30:00.26,0:30:04.88,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}放松一点~

Dialogue: 2,0:30:27.52,0:30:32.47,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}……原~来如此
Dialogue: 2,0:30:32.47,0:30:35.50,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}果~然

Dialogue: 2,0:30:35.50,0:30:46.77,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你是被歌姬芙·拉敏所~委托的啊~真伤脑筋啊~

Dialogue: 2,0:30:47.10,0:30:50.55,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}芙·拉敏~
Dialogue: 2,0:30:50.55,0:31:03.94,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}自那时开始~就对咒术有所执念，真伤脑筋啊~
Dialogue: 2,0:31:31.69,0:31:40.00,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}与去世之人~再度对话的方法~

Dialogue: 2,0:31:40.00,0:31:44.78,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}是~不存在的哦
Dialogue: 2,0:31:44.78,0:31:48.95,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}芙·拉敏小姐~

Dialogue: 2,0:31:49.34,0:31:56.61,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}他曾说乌尔达哈面临着危机
Dialogue: 2,0:31:56.61,0:32:03.90,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不调查清楚那危机是什么
Dialogue: 2,0:32:03.90,0:32:10.32,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不就没办法有对策吗？

Dialogue: 2,0:32:10.65,0:32:17.94,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}通过涅尔弗雷纳的调查
Dialogue: 2,0:32:17.94,0:32:28.63,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}知道他与阿希莉亚都是从阿拉米格而来的
Dialogue: 2,0:32:29.05,0:32:35.86,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}涅尔弗雷纳他们考虑
Dialogue: 2,0:32:35.86,0:32:44.23,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}他应该是带来了帝国的情报……

Dialogue: 2,0:32:44.56,0:32:50.48,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你是说他带来了~
Dialogue: 2,0:32:50.48,0:32:57.13,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}帝国即将进攻的通报~吗？

Dialogue: 2,0:32:57.13,0:33:07.29,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}所以被帝国的~间谍所~杀？

Dialogue: 2,0:33:08.69,0:33:14.62,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}但是~总之~

Dialogue: 2,0:33:14.62,0:33:19.31,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}那样的咒术是~
Dialogue: 2,0:33:19.31,0:33:24.85,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不存在的~
Dialogue: 2,0:33:24.98,0:33:27.62,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不过~

Dialogue: 2,0:33:27.62,0:33:34.26,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}因为那尸体是我们的东西~
Dialogue: 2,0:33:34.26,0:33:41.43,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}可以试着调查一番~

Dialogue: 2,0:33:41.59,0:33:47.32,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}买下了尸体？！

Dialogue: 2,0:33:47.32,0:33:53.45,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}为什么会？！
Dialogue: 2,0:33:53.64,0:33:56.87,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}好了好了
Dialogue: 2,0:33:56.87,0:34:07.58,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}去告诉议员大人也是没用的~

Dialogue: 2,0:34:07.91,0:34:14.10,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}而且我还帮过了忙~

Dialogue: 2,0:34:13.77,0:34:23.09,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}因为她没有她父亲的丧葬费~
Dialogue: 2,0:34:25.17,0:34:28.86,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}比起那个~
Dialogue: 2,0:34:28.86,0:34:33.71,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}比较实际的是~

Dialogue: 2,0:34:33.71,0:34:39.02,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}用咒术调查一下~
Dialogue: 2,0:34:39.02,0:34:47.23,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}那个叫做阿希莉亚的女孩的记忆啊~
Dialogue: 2,0:34:47.45,0:34:54.43,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}要是委托我的话~
Dialogue: 2,0:34:54.43,0:35:03.06,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我很高兴马上就着手哦~

Dialogue: 2,0:35:03.42,0:35:07.06,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不行啊
Dialogue: 2,0:35:07.06,0:35:14.82,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}咒术对年幼的孩子很危险
Dialogue: 2,0:35:14.82,0:35:23.06,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}绝对不能做那样的事
Dialogue: 2,0:36:02.57,0:36:04.95,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}怎么
Dialogue: 2,0:36:04.95,0:36:11.75,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你是冒险者吗？ 
Dialogue: 2,0:36:12.15,0:36:14.13,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}哼
Dialogue: 2,0:36:14.13,0:36:21.85,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}听说办了葬礼才过来看一眼
Dialogue: 2,0:36:21.85,0:36:29.77,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我还听说女孩死了父亲就剩下孤身一人……

Dialogue: 2,0:36:30.29,0:36:34.03,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}话说在前
Dialogue: 2,0:36:34.03,0:36:45.08,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}死去的可是与我无关的陌生男人啊！
Dialogue: 2,0:36:57.00,0:37:00.61,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}……原来如此~

Dialogue: 2,0:37:00.61,0:37:07.65,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你和这男子本就相识是吗~

Dialogue: 2,0:37:07.65,0:37:11.69,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}说起来你也是~
Dialogue: 2,0:37:11.69,0:37:17.55,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}阿拉米格出身的吧~

Dialogue: 2,0:37:17.91,0:37:23.87,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}是的，穆穆埃珀大人
Dialogue: 2,0:37:23.87,0:37:31.82,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}整理沃伯顿遗骸的任务
Dialogue: 2,0:37:31.82,0:37:36.41,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}请务必交给我
Dialogue: 2,0:37:36.64,0:37:44.98,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}造成这次事故的原因中也有我的责任
Dialogue: 2,0:37:45.24,0:37:49.96,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你心肠不错啊~
Dialogue: 2,0:37:49.96,0:37:56.25,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}虽然作为咒术师的话~
Dialogue: 2,0:37:56.25,0:38:00.39,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}那却是弱点~
Dialogue: 2,0:38:00.39,0:38:05.40,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}就交给你了吧~

Dialogue: 2,0:38:21.07,0:38:23.42,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}哦哦~
Dialogue: 2,0:38:23.42,0:38:27.98,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}让你久等了吗~

Dialogue: 2,0:38:27.98,0:38:36.90,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}那~、让我听听你的忏悔吧~
Dialogue: 2,0:38:41.17,0:38:43.64,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}那么~
Dialogue: 2,0:38:43.64,0:38:47.06,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}冒险者啊~

Dialogue: 2,0:38:47.06,0:38:52.44,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}继续刚才的话~
Dialogue: 2,0:38:52.44,0:38:54.93,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}实际上~
Dialogue: 2,0:38:54.93,0:39:02.37,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}是没有办法与死者交谈的~

Dialogue: 2,0:39:02.63,0:39:07.55,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}之所以有这个传闻~

Dialogue: 2,0:39:07.55,0:39:16.87,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}是因为在乌尔达哈的纳尔札尔教中~
Dialogue: 2,0:39:16.87,0:39:24.56,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}是有死者的世界存在的~

Dialogue: 2,0:39:24.78,0:39:26.78,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}当然
Dialogue: 2,0:39:26.78,0:39:30.84,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}招魂的方法~

Dialogue: 2,0:39:30.84,0:39:44.33,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}还在花费着很长很长时间去解开的途中~
Dialogue: 2,0:39:44.33,0:39:47.23,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}但是~
Dialogue: 2,0:39:47.23,0:39:59.31,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}还仍然没能找到啊~

Dialogue: 2,0:39:59.77,0:40:04.33,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}就是这样~

Dialogue: 2,0:40:04.33,0:40:10.94,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}虽然很抱歉~
Dialogue: 2,0:40:10.94,0:40:19.65,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}但我还是希望你能放弃~

Dialogue: 2,0:40:19.90,0:40:21.90,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不过~
Dialogue: 2,0:40:21.90,0:40:26.80,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你若是想精通咒术~

Dialogue: 2,0:40:26.80,0:40:32.37,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}然后去找出那个方法的话~
Dialogue: 2,0:40:32.37,0:40:40.35,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}请一定来成为这个阿达内斯圣柜堂的~
Dialogue: 2,0:40:40.35,0:40:43.68,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}咒术师学徒~

Dialogue: 2,0:40:44.13,0:40:50.06,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}有了秘藏之力的话~
Dialogue: 2,0:40:50.06,0:41:01.85,Yahei-1920x1080,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}就能通晓世间万物~
